# Login — obtain JWT token
#
# Prerequisite: user must be registered in the system.
# Response: copy the "access_token" field and use it in subsequent requests.
#
# Recommended extension: REST Client (humao.rest-client) for VS Code.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000

###

# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "dev@techword.local",
  "password": "DevTechWord2026!"
}

# Expected response (200 OK):
# {
#   "access_token": "eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9...",
#   "token_type": "bearer",
#   "expires_in": 900
# }
#
# Use the access_token in the Authorization header of protected requests:
#   Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.access_token}}
